<br>
There is a lot of FUN to be had in this game.. and this at any level!<br>
take your time and learn to feel comfortable with soloing, partnering and grouping..  <br>
make some dungeon crawls with a joint event of 2 groups.. <br>
<br>
I have played for more than 2 years and I am still at lvl 53. I took my time, I had tons of fun, and I learned a LOT about aggro management, pet control, solo tactics and group roles. I love the mage class, I love my pet, and I love my mana ;D<br>
<br>
soloing techniques?<br>
some where posted, but have you tried different ones? Solo just means you are alone with your pet.<br>
. dungeon crawling: get inside make a nice air pet...<br>
inch your way forward and watch the mobs, learn situational awareness, try to guess aggro ranges.. <br>
either you pull to you(less aggro) or send your DSed Pet into a room or corridor with mobs.... be sure to &quot;park&quot; (/pet guard here) your pet each time he is engaged in a fight (you want to gain territory inch by inch).. sit and med after each cleared piece of dungeon and keep mana high.<br>
use a water pet in SolB <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
. if you have a sow, pull with a large nuke, and circle a landmark in an oval track.....set your pet to /pet taunt off..  the mob will follow you, your water pet will follow the mob all the time whacking at its back.. be sure to nuke if you see your Mob attacking the pet instead of following you <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
there are so many possibilities..  and 5 different pets (monster pets in this count) to experiment with, they are all very good at something <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  discover it.<br>
<br>
<br>
level safely <p>daiquiri<br>
snail-footed magician 53<br>
Leader of Stone Circle<br>
