<br>
A) summon earth pet (preferred for root)<br>
B) DS Pet (not necessary, but helps a bit)<br>
C) Pull mob, send pet, pet roots and get's aggro<br>
D) Have a /pet report health hotkey made, punch it constantly<br>
E) Med, nuke at will, etc, til pet is at about 15-20 percent health<br>
F) Stand up, start casting pet<br>
G) Type, NOT HOTKEY, /pet get lost, wait til new pet spell is at about half a bubble til done casting, and hit enter to kill the pet<br>
H) Send new pet in, lather, rinse, repeat til death of mob<br>
<br>
The great thing about this is you get med time, and all you need is malachite and about as much mana as it takes you to cast your pet.<br>
<br>
Querlon Stormrage<br>
Mage of the 55th Summoning<br>
